In response, the applicant submitted a short video (2 minutes and 46 seconds long) showing:
1. The applicant speaking in Mandarin (46 seconds);
2. The applicant speaking in English stating his name, age and home town and briefly discussing his schooling, employment and family status (43 seconds);
3. The applicant's English tutor explaining that the applicant has learned basic English skills (17 seconds); and
4. The applicant displaying English writing skills by writing three short sentences: "I am Tang Xiao Feng. I am 35 years old. I am learning English now." (60 seconds).
